data.title: 以至少 50 个字回答问题
data.content: "If you could go back to a specific time in the past, what time period would you choose? Why? Give specific reasons for your answer."
data.answer: If I could go back to a specific time in the past, I would choose the age of 6 when I first entered primary school. The reason for my choice is that I regret not studying well and focusing on acquiring knowledge, which later on turned out to be essential in my life. In conclusion, as it is not possible for me to go back to primary school age, I will keep working to make sure that I do not regret it in the future. （85 字）
